Bubble sort, yan yana elemanlari karsilastirip gerekiyorsa yer degistirir. Her geciste en buyuk eleman sona 'kabarcik' gibi cikar:

def bubble_sort(arr):
    n = len(arr)
    for i in range(n):
        for j in range(n - i - 1):
            if arr[j] > arr[j + 1]:
                arr[j], arr[j + 1] = arr[j + 1], arr[j]
    return arr

sayilar = [64, 34, 25, 12, 22, 11, 90]
print(bubble_sort(sayilar))  # [11, 12, 22, 25, 34, 64, 90]

# Adim adim:
# [64, 34, 25, 12] -> [34, 64, 25, 12] -> [34, 25, 64, 12] -> [34, 25, 12, 64]
# Zaman karmasikligi: O(n^2) - yavas ama anlasilmasi kolay

