Go'da race condition var mi?
var bakiye int

func paraCek(miktar int) {
    if bakiye >= miktar {
        time.Sleep(time.Millisecond)
        bakiye -= miktar
    }
}

response:
Evet, race condition var. Mutex kullanilmali:

```go
import "sync"

type Hesap struct {
    mu     sync.Mutex
    bakiye int
}

func (h *Hesap) paraCek(miktar int) bool {
    h.mu.Lock()
    defer h.mu.Unlock()

    if h.bakiye >= miktar {
        h.bakiye -= miktar
        return true
    }
    return false
}
```

